column4: <content>Jean- Gabriel, Lemoine, Au Musée de Peinture de Bordeaux. Identifications. Remises au jour. Enrichissements, Bordeaux, 1942, p. 29.</content>

<part_of.title>Musée de Bordeaux as Bosch, discovered in 1940 by Mr. L. Jacobs van Merlen who thinks it to be by P. Bruegel the Elder, Panel, Diam. 15 cm; [toegevoegde vermelding]: 'F.G. Repainted? Judging by the photograph [opgeplakt], it may be by the same hand as the Bâilleur at Brussels, though it looks better.'</part_of.title>
